{"tid":1834291,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潤雄對年青人被捕感有點傷心","createTime":"2020-01-22T10:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T11:11:50.000Z","uid":138232,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"54c57c0c6a44dac198cb2165815791a8bf12b49f","tid":1834291,"uid":138232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:18:37.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】教育局局長楊潤雄指，反修例風波以來多名年青人被捕，涉及破壞、縱火案等，對此感到<span style=\"color: red;\">有點傷心</span>，反映教育有不足的地方。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄認為年青人較熱血，對社會事件感覺強，因此積極參與示威遊行，他認為有兩步可做，首先德育教育或需調節，其次是教學資源，可加強教導學生對錯觀念。<br />\n<br />\n他又指截至上月底，教育局收到147宗對教師的投訴，當中有32宗成立個案，部份涉網上仇恨言論、教材投訴，局方已發出警告信、譴責信、勸喻信等。"},{"pid":"1d57f943249a7791b1737b555ee04f8d58e3ac2c","tid":1834291,"uid":138232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:18:51.000Z","msg":"有點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8886d225967cf5f74687aa49cd8313b35089a2","tid":1834291,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:20:36.000Z","msg":"我對於你全家<br />\n就快遣返支那<br />\n感有點開心"},{"pid":"579559b1dd058f7b25b01d745a353290a2511ddb","tid":1834291,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d57f943249a7791b1737b555ee04f8d58e3ac2c","tid":1834291,"uid":138232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:18:51.000Z","msg":"有點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:23:31.000Z","msg":"楊局長同情暴徒會唔會唔係咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6590256f54d09cc46fcba9973e42083b347df686","tid":1834291,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:24:24.000Z","msg":"你全家成cancer 死我都會有點傷心"},{"pid":"27ba350143d2902e2144e993cf82ad67b6f26fcd","tid":1834291,"uid":338439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:25:09.000Z","msg":"你講乜都冇用，我要攬炒"},{"pid":"6e72771a9e36d2a9a8f747a617a40ce22cb891be","tid":1834291,"ui